<L>Bernard bere&thorn; witnesse &thorn;erfore,<NOTE PLACE="foot">DTL Seint B. witnessi&thorn; (L wittenessede) it (om. in L) before.</NOTE></L>
<L>Also do&thorn; hire Cosyn Ion:<NOTE PLACE="foot">D And so TL &amp; al-so. DL Iohn.</NOTE></L>
<L>ffor serwe &thorn;at heo hedde &thorn;ore<NOTE PLACE="foot">D sorwe TL &thorn;e sorwe. DT sche. D had TL hadde.</NOTE></L>
<L N="88">On swou&yogh; heo fel sone a-non.<NOTE PLACE="foot">D Out of hire eyen &thorn;e blod gan gone TL &thorn;e blod out of here (L hire) ey&yogh;en ron.</NOTE></L>
<L>&THORN;e blod out of hire e&yogh;en ron,<NOTE PLACE="foot">TL Out of here ey&yogh;en &thorn;e blod it (om. in L). DT ran.</NOTE></L>
<L>Al-most hire herte clef a-two&mdash;<NOTE PLACE="foot">L Almest. DT in two.</NOTE></L>
<L>Seynt Bernard, &thorn;at holy mon,<NOTE PLACE="foot">DTL &thorn;e holi man.</NOTE></L>
