<LG TYPE="stanza">
<L>"<NOTE PLACE="marg">vv. 201-8 added by the poet.</NOTE> Ladi," seide Bernard, "God &yogh;elde hit &thorn;e!<NOTE PLACE="foot">D Seyde Bernard Ladi I prey the T Lefdy quod B. y praye &thorn;e L Swete lauedy pray I &thorn;e.</NOTE></L>
